  "content": [
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Lionel Messi was born in Rosario, Argentina and grew up there and in Barcelona, Spain."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.tribune.com.ng/sun/church-features/1588-pre-match-prayer-who-does-god-answer",
      "sourceTitle": "Pre-match prayer Who does God answer?",
      "text": "Messi is a Catholic,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "but his religious views are not something he talks much about, or at all for that matter."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QK-JU9QIs4I",
      "sourceTitle": "Lionel Messi Converted To Islam 2011-2012[MUST SEE]",
      "text": "Interestingly, an Islamic news organization reported that Messi had converted to Islam."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Their sources were unconfirmed and Messi never even bothered to speak out about it. Nevertheless, rumors now abound that Messi is a Muslim. My sense of things is that he's still a Catholic."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": "A face for politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.lionel-messi.co.uk/news/messi-features-wrongly-in-political-campaign.html",
      "sourceTitle": "Messi Features Wrongly in Political Campaign",
      "text": "Messi isn't really political himself, he just tends to be used by politicians–sometimes without his permission. A photo of Messi was used by politician Alfredo Olmedo of Salta, Argentina with the caption (loosely translated): Say yes to sports, say no to drugs."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Messi pursued legal action against Olmedo."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.excellence2012.dk/news/show/artikel/lionel-messi-helps-to-open-eu-conference/",
      "sourceTitle": "Lionel Messi helps to open EU conference",
      "text": "Also, Messi's likeness was used at an EU political conference, but only as an example of an excellent European"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "even though he's really Argentinian."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "If Messi has any actual political views (and I'm sure he does), he manages to keep them out of the spotlight–which might be for the better as he's a football hero to most people, not a social commentator."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
